<article>
  <h1>Installing DITA-OT</h1>

  <p>You need Java 17+ installed first.</p>

  <ol>
    <li>Go to https://www.dita-ot.org/download</li>
    <li>Download the latest .zip release</li>
    <li>Unzip to a directory (e.g., ~/dita-ot)</li>
    <li>Add ~/dita-ot/bin to your PATH</li>
    <li>Test: run <code>dita --version</code></li>
  </ol>

  <p>If you see the version number, you're all set!</p>
</article>
